# Presence of this file enables host docker socket forwarding for the project.
# Content is ignored — sbx only checks that the file exists.
#
# WARNING: mounting the host docker socket grants root-equivalent access to
# the host. Anything in the container can break out via `docker run --privileged`.
# Only enable for projects you trust.
#
# Toggle with: sbx config docker on  /  sbx config docker off
